{"type": "item.completed", "item": {"id": "item_1", "type": "command_execution", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc 'cat status.md'", "aggregated_output": "# Grace \u2014 Status\n\n## Current Task\nT816 \u2014 Sprint 6: Phase 1 live-data fixture + validation pack\n\n## Progress\n- [x] Read `status.md`, `../../public/knowledge.md`, inbox audit notes, and Bob's Sprint 6 normalization contract\n- [x] Refactored `output/grace/market_filter.js` to normalize live-shaped Kalshi payloads and surface rejected-invalid markets explicitly\n- [x] Created sanitized fixture pack, expected-output contract, and runnable verifier for Phase 1\n- [x] Ran verification and generated fresh T816 artifacts\n- [x] Moved T816 to `in_review` and sent handoff messages with artifact path, run command, and freshness marker\n- [x] Hardened `verify_live_phase1_fixture.js` with case-level outcome assertions, low-volume contract checks, and timestamp-order validation\n\n## Decisions Log\n- [2026-04-07] Decision: Keep T816 artifacts on new Sprint 6-specific paths instead of overwriting `filtered_markets.json`. Reason: preserve the Sprint 4 T579 review artifact while shipping a clean live-readiness pack.\n- [2026-04-07] Decision: Reuse Bob's `live_market_normalizer` inside Grace's Phase 1 filter. Reason: keep the live payload contract consistent across Sprint 6 and reject malformed inputs at the boundary.\n- [2026-04-07] Decision: Add explicit semantic sanity checks for unemployment, bitcoin dominance, and Solana thresholds in the verifier. Reason: Ivan's T815 audit found implausible numeric titles and this prevents recurrence before T236.\n- [2026-04-07] Decision: Assert per-ticker expected outcomes and freshness ordering inside the verifier. Reason: aggregate summary checks alone could miss case regressions or stale fixture/output mismatches.\n\n## Blockers\n- Waiting on reviewer approval for T816 (`in_review`)\n\n## Recent Activity\n- [2026-04-07 07:20 PDT] Claimed T816 and moved it to `in_progress`\n- [2026-04-07 07:24 PDT] Generated `output/grace/filtered_markets_live_fixture.json` and `output/grace/live_phase1_validation_report.md` via `node output/grace/verify_live_phase1_fixture.js`\n- [2026-04-07 07:24 PDT] Sent review and handoff notes to Olivia, Alice, and Ivan with freshness markers\n- [2026-04-07 09:15 PDT] Re-ran `node ../../output/grace/verify_live_phase1_fixture.js` after adding case-by-case outcome checks, low-volume exclusions contract, and fixture/output timestamp validation\n", "exit_code": 0, "status": "completed"}}
